select_place_address_details.query: SELECT a.*, sat.name as address_type FROM mod_address a LEFT OUTER JOIN sys_address_type sat ON a.sys_address_type_id = sat.id LEFT OUTER JOIN sys_address_link mal ON mod_address_id = a.id AND mal.object_type = 'place' AND mal.object_id = :mod_place_id WHERE sat.name = 'Venue address' ORDER BY a.label
